# intraday-x — copy to `.env` and fill in. NEVER commit your real .env (it's gitignored).

# --- Alpaca (free tier; the multi-year 1-minute backtest backbone) -----------
# Sign up free at https://alpaca.markets/  (no funding needed for market data).
# Generate keys in the dashboard: https://app.alpaca.markets/  → API Keys.
# The free IEX feed works with paper-trading keys; the composite provider auto-
# prefers Alpaca over yfinance for deep history once these are set.
ALPACA_API_KEY=
ALPACA_SECRET_KEY=

# --- Polygon.io (optional upgrade; full-market intraday vs Alpaca's IEX slice) -
# Free tier at https://polygon.io/ (~2yr, 5 req/min). If set, the composite
# router auto-prefers Polygon. No code needed — the provider is already wired.
POLYGON_API_KEY=

# --- Frontend (optional) -----------------------------------------------------
# In dev the Vite proxy forwards /api + /ws to the backend on :8000, so no env
# is required. For a split deployment, point the dashboard at the API:
# PUBLIC_API_BASE=https://your-api-host
# PUBLIC_WS_URL=wss://your-api-host/ws/signals
